– Let's dig in!
– Let's dig in!

186
00:09:05.900 --> 00:09:07.320
– What the hell?!
– What the hell?!

187
00:09:07.320 --> 00:09:09.490
What?! My hands pass right through it!

188
00:09:09.490 --> 00:09:10.530
What is this?!

189
00:09:11.530 --> 00:09:13.280
It's there, but I can't grab it!

190
00:09:13.280 --> 00:09:15.620
It's making me even hungrier!

191
00:09:15.620 --> 00:09:18.250
I can't eat it!

192
00:09:20.920 --> 00:09:22.460
Don't tell me, we...

193
