have food laying out in the open.

207
00:10:00.450 --> 00:10:03.120
Still, this is my first time seeing a hologram.

208
00:10:03.120 --> 00:10:05.290
What the hell?! They're gonna pay!

209
00:10:05.670 --> 00:10:08.420
A three-dimensional image produced by light.

210
00:10:08.420 --> 00:10:11.550
It's like something out of
a comic strip or fantasy world.

211
00:10:11.550 --> 00:10:12.590
An image?!

212
00:10:13.800 --> 00:10:16.930
So that's why I passed
through that space monster!

213
00:10:16.930 --> 00:10:19.180
That giant robot must be a hologram, as well.

214
00:10:19.180 --> 00:10:21.770
